description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-22-2013 FRI




The Glenn Beck Program




Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
November 22, 2013 10:21 AM



It has been 50 years since President John F. Kennedy was struck down
    in his motorcade through Dallas Texas.

  Guest Brad Meltzer joins Glenn and company to talk about all the theories that still
     to this day surround the assassination.


  Also it's Friday and that means More-on Trivia.
